Package fr.reflexe.viewshell.api.data.types

Specialized interfaces for handling data types.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IArrayData
    Provides typed access to an array dataset for a cell.
    IArrayItem
    Provides access to a single data record managed by an array dataset contained by a parent data structure.
    IArrayType
    Cell data type representing an embedded set of child items attached as an array to a parent item.
    IBinaryData
    Provides typed access to binary data for a cell, such as files.
    IBinaryType
    Cell data type representing a binary data value, such as a file stored in a database, or a serialized object.
    IBooleanData
    Provides typed access to boolean data for a cell.
    IBooleanType
    Cell data type representing a boolean data value.
    IDateData
    Provides typed access to date data for a cell.
    IDateTimeData
    Provides typed access to date with time data for a cell.
    IDateTimeType
    Cell data type representing a date with time value.
    IDateType
    Cell data type representing a date value (without the time of day).
    IDecimalData
    Provides typed access to decimal number data for a cell.
    IDecimalType
    Cell data type representing a decimal number type.
    IFloatData
    Provides typed access to IEEE 754 floating point number data for a cell.
    IFloatType
    Cell data type representing an IEEE 754 floating point number type.
    IImageData
    Provides typed access to image data for a cell.
    IImageType
    Cell data type representing a binary image type, such as a picture.
    IIntegerData
    Provides typed access to integer number data for a cell.
    IIntegerType
    Cell data type representing an integer number type.
    INumberType
    Cell base type for all numeric data types.
    IRelationData
    Provides access to relationship data values.
    IRelationType
    Cell data type representing a relationship between entities, such as a foreign key (for a relational database) or a link relationship (for a graph database).
    ITextData
    Provides typed access to text data for a cell, such as simple strings or text-based documents.
    ITextType
    Cell data type for text types.
    ITimeData
    Provides typed access to time (without date) data for a cell.
    ITimeType
    Cell data type representing a time value (without the date and therefore with no time zone information).
    IUuidData
    Provides typed access to UUID data for a cell.
    IUuidType
    Cell data type representing a UUID data value.

Package fr.reflexe.viewshell.api.data.types Description

Specialized interfaces for handling data types.

Most interfaces in this package extend the base interfaces for data types and values.

Since:
1.0
